FIG. 7B is a view showing a conventional chip handling method;


FIGS. 8A to 8C are views showing a conventional method for mounting a bare chip on a carrier by soldering; and


FIG. 9 is a view showing a conventional method for mounting a bare chip on a carrier with an interposer in between.
